window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Danger Triumph and Glory.</p> <p>When another Nether Portal opens in the kingdom legends die, and new ones are born.</p> <p>Koen is accepted into the famous Dragon Stone Academy, where he'll certainly encounter adventure, magic, and power beyond his wildest dreams. None of it comes easy though, and as he learns, he'll uncover more than he expected. Secrets lurk deep within the kingdom and its fabled academy. Some of them are eager to keep a young hero from saving the world.</p>"; 
